WPS Architecture Section
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

 In this section you can find description of the 52North WPS Architecture.
 
 	
 	
 The basic architecture is depicted in the following figure
 
 [images/Architecture.png] figure 1
 
 Basically, all external data formats are mapped to an internal dataformat via so called "Parser".
 The internal dataformat is consumed by the process itself.